Description:
This plugin will enable you to place a tag cloud of related tags on the items browse page.

This is version 0.1 of this plugin and was tested on version 1.3.2 of OMEKA.

Instructions:
1. Upload and install the RelatedTagCloud plugin into your plugins folder on the server, see: (Installing a Plugin).
2. Activate this from the Plugins page in your admin panel: /admin=>Settings=>Plugins.

The plugin will generate a tag cloud, it will collect tags from items that have tags in common with the items on the browse page.

RelatedTagCloud and Other Plugins:
Keep in mind that if you are activating other plugins that append the items/browse page for displaying content those elements may crowd the page's public display.